  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a957bfb8-cdae-4327-821d-f43d20a1b3ba\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-02a579b8-d869-44c2-81ca-f576fea94bee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5e54bb78-99d2-4bf9-96e0-cfbabce9c31c\">안녕하세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c813b6dc-898f-45f6-bf39-ee01bfa9b67f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-72ba2598-9eba-49fc-ba0c-39fcbc64af44\">7호선 남성역 1번출구 앞 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7f7a5648-63d2-4aa5-b248-c20493ac0bac\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-65b3ac77-399c-4bd3-afee-b187b7231343\">이수한의원입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4f2cb91a-19cf-41bd-8745-590f54daa4d6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-20ac05a0-28ce-4ebb-943f-baf1a9f545e8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0673ce5e-882c-4bc6-9cb3-fc35a9db83ca\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9986ed30-2d7c-41a2-b0d7-96a6163b6a99\">엉치가 아프고 다리가 땡기고 저리는 증상을 경험해 본 적이 있으신가요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b6771298-4276-42a8-a0fc-cfd3abe7212f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5836156b-5d07-4eed-91ec-60f559fb16ce\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1beaacff-033b-4435-a802-7ba00fc2195c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7ad20a3a-2587-4d8b-a99b-6abbf2a55bf4\">발걸음 딛을 때마다 엉치가 시큰거리고 아팠던 경험은요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2c87e83e-cb13-4515-9ca4-f41866adb7a7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ea936de2-31a5-4732-8663-36877dbc8894\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2e395e52-b208-46e9-9323-b9e442d7a5b5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6bf599fc-a252-48fb-8870-4f61c4874955\">허리가 아팠는데, 시간이 지나면서 아픈 부위가 엉치 허벅지로 옮겨 가진 않던가요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-56459e17-f022-4f46-8a05-aae46e78fcb8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2eed4b31-eb26-434b-97a3-29950e996139\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e40bc36d-fd52-4e47-a834-fc41e5ad676a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-498414bf-86a4-4b57-b377-20a22cdbc67c\">이런 경우 원인은 허리에 있는 경우가 많습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fa83c9fb-01e3-431e-9c35-01c5abf893c9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e80a7ba8-6cf9-4bbe-99ea-26ee78d319eb\">허리에서 신경이 눌리면서 엉치 다리로 뻗어가는 신경 따라 통증이 느껴지는 거죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9441c3ef-0962-4461-a0c9-1b20a5511071\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9394ef46-ca74-4cc1-a9e8-ffba2582f12e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n              